title: Farcry 1 [COMPLETO] [5 PARTES] [ISO] By Brand's
description:
FAR CRY 1 DISC 5 PARTS

Far Cry is a high quality shooting game that takes place in the jungles and pristine beaches of the Pacific Ocean islands. Mercenaries, ships, weapons and a lot of action on this kind of Counter-Striketropical.

Far Cry The argument goes as follows: You are Jack Carver, captain of a ship that carries passengers and freight through the crystal clear waters of the Pacific. The arrival of a group of mercenaries, complicates matters and you must fight to defend the ship and keep it under control.

Even if the graphics are a bit outdated (Far Cry was released in 2004), the landscapes, movements and effects are very well maintained and can transport you to Polynesia. Also install Far Cry Patch to correct errors and bugs.

Step into the shoes of Jack Carver and relive all the excitement of this classic shooter games.
